      <title>預覽 日本央行預計通膨將維持在目標附近，預示有升息機會</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/boj-project-inflation-will-stay-around-target-signal-chance-rate-hike-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行預計將在周五發布的新預測中預測未來三年通膨率將保持在 2% 左右的目標附近，這表明日本央行準備今年從目前接近零的水平再次升息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/boj-project-inflation-will-stay-around-target-signal-chance-rate-hike-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
